##################################
# PDFs (choose ONE option)
##################################

# Option A: Ignore all PDFs (recommended if PDFs are build outputs)
# *.pdf

# Option B: Track PDFs, but ignore common generated ones
# Uncomment if you *do* want final PDFs versioned
# !*.pdf

